After a hectic day of shooting, especially if you're shooting outdoor in this weather, it's super important to have good food afterwards!
I visited @theburgerclubin in Connaught Place and had the Spicy Chicken Club Burger!
I have to say, it was absolutely DELICIOUS..🍔
Perfect size, filling and doesn't burn a hole in your pocket! 👍🏻👍🏻 I really found @theburgerclubin very reasonable in terms of price, really good taste and great ambience too! 👌🏻
Highly recommend from my side.. must visit! 😍
